<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= videoTitle %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/athletes.css"> 
    <%- include('partials/google-analytics') %>
    
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .video-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh; 
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%; 
            box-sizing: border-box;
            
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); 
            text-align: center;
        }
        .video-player {
            max-width: 90%; 
            max-height: 80vh;
            width: 100%;
            border: 3px solid #ffc400;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 196, 0, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .video-title {
            color: #ffc400;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
            word-break: break-word; 
        }
        .button-back {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ffc400;
            color: #111111;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button-back:hover {
            background-color: #ffd966;
        }
        
        .bottom-bar {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="video-container">
        <div class="video-title"><%= videoTitle %></div>
        
        <video controls class="video-player" poster="/images/video-poster.jpg">
            <source src="/videos/<%= videoFile %>" type="video/mp4">
            Ваш браузер не поддерживает видео тег.
        </video>
        
        <a href="/athletes" class="button-back">← Вернуться к материалам</a>
    </div>
    
    </body>
</html>